VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'Pin yourself to v0.1.4 or later, and you skip most of them. Provider support is generous. Anthropic for Claude, OpenAI for GPT. Gemini for Google. DeepSeek, Kimiko, GLM for the China stack. Ollama'

[04:36] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'for fully local. Open Router and Silicon Flow for aggregator routing. And a generic OpenAI-compatible endpoint for anything else. LM Studio, vLLM, your own deployment. You bring your own key for'

